import React from 'react'
import { closeicon, icon, sidebarcontainer } from './sidebarelement'

const Sidebar = () => {
    return (
        <sidebarcontainer>
            <icon>
                <closeicon />
            </icon>
        </sidebarcontainer>
    )
}
<icon>
    <closeicon />
</icon>
export default Sidebar
